es%2F&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=b56e08b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.politifact.com/factchecks/2020/dec/02/ron-desantis/florida-doing-better-covid-19-locked-down-states/</a><br />\n<br />\nIF YOUR TIME IS SHORT<br />\n&bull; Currently, Florida has relatively low rates of coronavirus cases, deaths and hospitalizations. However, the connection between this and Florida&rsquo;s light regulation of businesses&rsquo; and residents&rsquo; behavior is less clear-cut than DeSantis suggests.<br />\n<br />\n&bull; Only about half of the 10 most stringently regulated states saw rates of cases, deaths and hospitalizations that were twice as high as Florida&rsquo;s, which was DeSantis&rsquo; benchmark.<br />\n<br />\n&bull; Numerous other states that followed similarly low-regulation policies are seeing coronavirus statistics far worse than Florida&rsquo;s. This means Florida&rsquo;s lower infection numbers could be related to factors other than behavioral regulations, such as its warmer weather."},{"pid":"c52db74231fa5de8e66d9b3980a20b3544aee0c1","tid":2398454,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f01fbf34ee12a42f7e786d1beb87aea6d7d3e3dc","tid":2398454,"uid":387461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"其實隻毒係好廢<br />\n咁係呢度祝樓主全家中曬 <br />\n老豆中完惹比老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n連登仔咪成日開PO笑黑警中武肺仲要開香檳慶祝既<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝就慶完啦<br />\n死左幾多個呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔要幾時先識醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a125ff99f7106ddfcb087fbf7f8ea5c852cac655","tid":2398454,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0db44348c6d1a917069229ef8bcf974a7092f433","tid":2398454,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid